comment: Thompson (CLE) makes contact with Lowry (TOR) before he has gathered the ball, affecting his SQBR. On a drive to the rim that will end in the Lower Defensive Box, contact must occur after the gather to be deemed a shooting foul.
Korver (CLE) cleanly dislodges the ball away from DeRozan (TOR), and then maintains a legal guarding position in the corner.
James (CLE) steps forward to contest Ibaka's (TOR) shot, and then turns, leaving his left foot in Ibaka's landing area.
After communicating with the Replay Center, James (CLE) is assessed a common foul. James is turning and not extending his leg forward into Ibaka's (TOR) landing area. 01:42.1 01:42.1
Valanciunas (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with James (CLE) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt. 01:32.1 01:32.1

After Love (CLE) secures the rebound, DeRozan (TOR) makes contact with his arms and wraps him up. Love steps with the ball, however when a violation (like a travel) and a foul occur at the same time, the foul will take precedence.

Love (CLE) swings his elbows and makes contact with DeRozan (TOR). Given the wind up and impact, the play should have been reviewed and a Flagrant Foul Penalty 1 should have been assessed. 01:11.1 01:11.1
Anunoby (TOR) establishes a wide screening position in Smith's (CLE) path, but contact occurs to Anunoby's torso area and not his leg.
James (CLE) cleanly steals the ball from DeRozan (TOR). Period 00:31.0 00:31.0
Lowry (TOR) establishes a screening position in James's (CLE) path before contact, leaning forward and extending his arms, but collapses his arms and absorbs the contact from James.
Hill (CLE) keeps consistent hand contact on DeRozan (TOR) without affecting his SQBR. LHH shows that Hill's hand brushes DeRozan's loose jersey and he does not grab it.
[Incidental or immaterial] Valanciunas (TOR) dislodges Thompson (CLE) while the ball is in the air and Thompson holds Valanciunas' jersey. Neither player makes an attempt for the rebound.
Thompson (CLE) makes incidental contact with Miles' (TOR) body on the follow-through.
As Valanciunas (TOR) puts the ball back, James (CLE) initiates contact to his side. LATR and RATR show that James extends his arm slightly, but does not affect Valanciunas' shot attempt.
Prior to the inbound pass, James (CLE) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR). 02:03.1 02:03.1
In coming to a stop, Thompson (CLE) gathers the ball on his left foot, then steps with his right to establish a pivot foot. He leaves his pivot foot on the floor until he releases his pass.
RATR shows that DeRozan (TOR) dislodges Thompson (CLE), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound. 01:31.1 01:31.1
Smith (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position and remains vertical as he contests DeRozan's (TOR) driving shot attempt. 01:22.1 01:22.1
RATR shows Thompson (CLE) establishes a legal picking position in Anunoby's (TOR) path before contact and both players move along the same path after the initial pick. 01:01.1 01:01.1
Love (CLE) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt. Period 00:58.0 00:58.0
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Cavaliers possession is confirmed.
DeRozan (TOR) and Korver (CLE) engage and disengage.

LATR shows that James (CLE) draws DeRozan (TOR) into the air, but that DeRozan does not make contact with him after James-- starts his shooting motion. DeRozan then turns and makes contact with the ball, cleanly blocking James' shot.
Correctly called 24 second violation. 00:03.5
Valanciunas (TOR) and Smith (CLE) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
James (CLE) and Lowry (TOR) make incidental contact as they both attempt to secure the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that the foul by DeRozan (TOR) occurs prior to the expiration of the game clock.
DeRozan (TOR) commits a take foul on Thompson (CLE). Event Assessments: CC = Correct Call, IC = Incorrect Call, CNC = Correct Non-Call, INC = Incorrect Non-Call
